Type of Feat: General
Your song or poetics echo the power of the dragonsong, an ancient style of vocal performance created by dragons in the distant past.
Prerequisite: Cha 13, Lore 4, Perform 6, Bard Songs
Benefit: You gain a +2 bonus with the Perform skill as well as +2 to the DC of any bardic music effects.
Affected songs: Cloud Mind, Fascinate, and Inspire Slowing.
Use: Automatic.